metadata.name: Foodles Serum
metadata.description: A community-driven project aiming to develop a creative incubator to empower female creators and artists. Foodles Club come in a joyful range of colors, traits, and sizes with a collection size of 5000. Foodles Club holders can participate in exclusive events such as NFT claims, raffles, community giveaways and charity fundraisers; the community will determine our future!
